title: Whats Next For Cuba
itunes:title: Whats Next For Cuba
description: Since out shows on Cuba have been so popular, we will discuss what the future holds for Cuba and Cuban Cigars. This week the state department made the move to remove Cuba from the list of counties that support terrorism.We will all way in with out thoughts as to what will happen next on the Island of South of the Mainland.We will also discuss the TAA which happens next week and our own David Garofalo will be there!﻿
